@{PARD}
@{B}Blue Goon Combat:@{UB}@{PAR}

Blue goons typically attack with whatever weapons they can make, usually crude
clubs and spears. The fumes coming out of their mouths are not harmful. They are
fairly strong, having an average strength of about 16.@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Habitat" "Blue Goon Habitat/Society"
@{CODE}	@{" Picture         " LINK "ImpPro:Data/ExtMonsterData/Blue Goon.iff/main"}@{" Stats           " LINK "Stats"}
