@{PARD}
@{B}Blue Goon Habitat/Society:@{UB}@{PAR}

Blue goons are very warlike. They kill anything which they can find, except
members of their own tribe. It is not uncommon to see tribes of Blue goons
fighting with each other.@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Ecology" "Blue Goon Ecology"
@{CODE}	@{" Picture         " LINK "ImpPro:Data/ExtMonsterData/Blue Goon.iff/main"}@{" Stats           " LINK "Stats"}
	@{" Combat          " LINK "Combat"}@{" Habitat/Society " LINK "Habitat"}@{" Ecology         " LINK "Ecology"}

@{PARD}
@{B}Blue Goon Ecology:@{UB}@{PAR}

Blue goons kill whatever they see. Although they have no "natural" enemies, they
are constantly at war. They occasionally raid neighboring tribes for food and
weapons.@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

